{"tid":1446301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好亂同人講野","createTime":"2019-08-11T14:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:05:14.000Z","uid":236505,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5eb344c54d9a4e85c37844365852e8a9bef807a1","tid":1446301,"uid":236505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:53:29.000Z","msg":"現場唔單止前線有鬼<br />\n中線 後線 咩地方都會有鬼<br />\n所以一定要結伴而行<br />\n遇到有人問你去邊 <br />\n一陣有咩計劃 <br />\n甚至係電話 身份證等個人資料<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記得一句野都唔好講</span><br />\n求其fake走佢就算<br />\n因為太多人無危機意識<br />\n好易比鬼呃<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好比祈福黨呃到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff2af97046030a148eb62fb0aec6dd075e3fd1e","tid":1446301,"uid":236505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:53:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3f2aedc5acf83e23c0d5ec161d27c0f74f332ca","tid":1446301,"uid":236505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:54:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d3929efdf2b912033958f2e36300169c4a0e6e35","tid":1446301,"uid":236505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:54:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9f98c265e3d09ee9498d6b65d7668b1e5b7d570","tid":1446301,"uid":236505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:54:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d84d3119df6e5e967e60a75ed7c3a74e059973e2","tid":1446301,"uid":236505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:54:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d67e41e740d7b56913158a431d3c50170b2c5b9","tid":1446301,"uid":236505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:55:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"233476662a72f9e76c021775d3743b9639f75410","tid":1446301,"uid":236505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:55:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"283d596c7a0bd27b3c82e88eb2e10274f6f0acff","tid":1446301,"uid":236505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:5